# 00‑project‑overview\.mdc

## Project: **Qur’an & Sunnah Companion (Chrome Extension)**

**Mission ✨**
Deliver a lightweight, privacy‑respectful popup that puts Qur’an recitation, Sahih Hadith, and Dhikr reminders one click away—without navigating away from the current tab.

**Elevator pitch**
“Your pocket‑size īmān boost in every tab.”

**Version 1 scope**

* Manifest V3 Chrome/Edge extension, popup only (no content scripts)
* Vanilla **HTML 5**, **CSS 3** (Flexbox + CSS Grid), **ES 2022 modules**
* English ↔ Arabic UI switcher (Chrome `i18n`)
* Reciters: Mishary, Abdul Basit, Minshawi, Al‑Hussary, Bandar Balila, Badr Turki, Maher al‑Muaiqly, Muhammad Refat, Ali Jabir, Mohamed Ayoub
* Free public APIs (no keys): api.quran.com, hadithapi.com, fitrahive/dua‑dhikr JSON

**North‑star metrics**

| Metric                        | Target   |
| ----------------------------- | -------- |
| Install → 1st play conversion | ≥ 70 %   |
| 7‑day retained users          | ≥ 25 %   |
| Average daily playback        | ≥ 10 min |
| Web Store rating              | ≥ 4.5⭐   |

